parameters.name: DomainName
parameters.description: The ingest domain. You can specify only one domain in each request.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description:
Get the log end time.
Date format follows the ISO8601 representation and uses UTC+0 time, formatted as yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: \[1,1000]. Default value: 300.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: Get the log start time in ISO8601 format with UTC+0 timezone, formatted as yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ.
